snippet.title: Super Potato Bruh Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Get it here: https://cmlsc.itch.io/super-potato-bruh 

Super Potato Bruh is a bullet hell platformer with lots of pixel art! It takes inspiration from Super Mario Bros, Super Meat Boy, and Geometry Dash. It doesn't take inspiration from any bullet hell in particular, just the genre.
